<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.3.8">
<l>kuṟikkoṇ ñāṉaṅkaḷā leṉaiyūḻi ceytavamuṅ</l>
<l>kiṟikkoṇ ṭippiṟappē cilanāḷi leytiṉaṉyā</l>
<l>ṉuṟikkoṇṭa veṇṇeypā loḷittuṇṇu mammāṉpi</l>
<l>ṉeṟikkoṇṭa neñcaṉāyp piṟavit tuyarkaṭintē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is all the penance done for aeons with tenacious knowledge?</l>
<l>Playing pranks for myself I have reached [the goal] in this birth in a few days,</l>
<l>chasing the misery of birth as one whose heart takes the path</l>
<l>after the lord how secretly ate the butter [and] milk that were taken from the pot net.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
